<B>__{whoop.}
<A>__{lights flashing, the police car makes a right turn from the left lane, cutting in front of them. the siren is deafening. simon sees his opportunity. gunning the engine, he hangs a hard left, cutting across three oncoming lanes. the ram charger tries to follow, but the traffic is already moving. over the protest of many horns, the pickup finally forces its way through.}
